meta.desc: App-Switcher modification that sorts applications by current workspace first. It separates apps into 2 separate icons if the app also has windows on other workspaces.
meta.desc_long: App-Switcher modification that sorts applications by current workspace first. It separates apps into 2 separate icons if the app also has windows on other workspaces.
